==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incognizant
<hw>In*cog"ni*zant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not cognizant;
failing to apprehended or notice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Of the several operations themselves, as acts of volition, we are
wholly <qex>incognizant</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W.
Hamilton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incognoscible</ent>⟦br⟧
